_sText: Map I made where you can drive or shoot out of a total of 6 "tanks" (2 large one s with 2 guns and 4 small ones with 1 gun). You spawn with m4a1, deagle, he nade, and smoke. The goal is simply to kill that the other team using any means possible. Has 2 destructable buildings to use as cover. Very fun to charge the enemy in a tanks and have your gunner try to kill them before you get killed.
